## Data Flow
- Frontend Web (React) serves UI, language toggles, and voice interaction.
- Frontend Web calls Backend API via HTTP for:
  - Authentication (`/api/auth/*`)
  - Voice field extraction (`/api/voice/process`)
  - Profile creation + recommendations (`/api/auth/create-profile`)
  - Job listing and posting (`/api/jobs`)
- Backend API persists and queries MongoDB (via Mongoose) for `AuthUser`, `User` (profile), and `Job` collections.
- Optional AI chat responses are generated via Gemini API when invoked.

